{"word":"συμμαχέω","slug":"συμμαχέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>συμμαχέω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>ήσω</el>) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:σύμμαχος'><el>σύμμαχος</el></a>\n<p/><i>to be an ally, to be in alliance</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>:—generally, <i>to help, aid, succour</i>, <el>τινί</el> <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be assisted</i>, <b><a href='S:Lucian'>Luc.</a></b><p/>"}]}